---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import SplitSection from "../SplitSection.astro";
import Ecrevisse2Image from "../../assets/images/clos-des-sens-juillet-2023-plats-ecrevisse2.jpg";
import HaricotsImage from "../../assets/images/clos-des-sens-septembre-2021-plats-haricots3.jpg";
import FenouilleImage from "../../assets/images/clos-des-sens-septembre-2021-plat-fenouille6.jpg";
---

<SplitSection
  title="Un moment"
  bgColor="#251715"
  isInverted
>
  Par le prisme culinaire, entre pudeur et force vitale, le monde du vivant
  s'exprime jusqu'à la quintessence. Sublimé, il livre son émotion ultime.
  <div slot="right" class="w-full h-full relative overflow-hidden">
    <Image src={Ecrevisse2Image} alt="Ecrevisse" class="moment-slide" />
    <Image src={HaricotsImage} alt="Haricots" class="moment-slide" />
    <Image src={FenouilleImage} alt="Fenouilles" class="moment-slide" />
  </div>
</SplitSection>

<style>
  .moment-slide {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: -100%;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    animation: momentSlideShow 18s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes momentSlideShow {
    0% {
      left: -100%;
    }
    16.67% {
      left: 0;
    }
    33.34% {
      left: 0;
    }
    50% {
      left: 100%;
    }
    100% {
      left: 100%;
    }
  }

  .moment-slide:nth-child(1) {
    animation-delay: -3s;
  }

  .moment-slide:nth-child(2) {
    animation-delay: 3s;
  }

  .moment-slide:nth-child(3) {
    animation-delay: 9s;
  }
</style>
